title: Thinking in React
subtitle: 5 day workshop
description: Thinking in React. React is a web framework. But it's also a new way of thinking. Mastering this way of thinking is the key to success with React. JavaScript update: Modern React apps make heavy use of advanced and newer JavaScript techniques, such as class fields, arrow functions, spread operators, functional programming techniques, modules and build systems.  React API in depth. We'll cover all of the details needed to use React in production applications. React Ecosystem. One of React's strong points is the robust React ecosystem. But this can also be one of the scariest parts of React. In this workshop, we provide an up-to-date, curated set of recomendations for which libraries and tools to use, when to use them and how to use them.
